<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Fmt on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/fmt/</link><description>Recent content in Fmt on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/fmt/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] C++ fmt - formatting error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/fmt-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/fmt-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="fmt---formatting-error"&gt;fmt - formatting error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The fmt library throws errors when format strings are invalid, arguments don&amp;rsquo;t match placeholders, or types are unsupported.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Wrong argument count
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; s &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, {} and {}!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// too few args
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Invalid format syntax
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; s &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, {name!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// missing closing brace
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Wrong type
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; s &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;{:d}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;not a number&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// wrong format specifier
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-match-argument-count"&gt;Fix 1: Match argument count&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; s &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, {} and {}!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Bob&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-fix-format-syntax"&gt;Fix 2: Fix format syntax&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; s &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, {name}!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;arg(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-use-correct-format-specifiers"&gt;Fix 3: Use correct format specifiers&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; s &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;{:.2f}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3.14159&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// correct for float
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; s &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;{:d}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;42&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// correct for int
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/spdlog-error/"&gt;spdlog - logging error&lt;/a&gt; — logging errors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/fmt-error/"&gt;fmt format error (detailed)&lt;/a&gt; — detailed fmt errors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/ios-base-failure/"&gt;std::ios_base::failure&lt;/a&gt; — stream errors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] C++ std::format Error — Format String Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/format-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/format-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="solution-c-stdformat-error--format-string-fix"&gt;[Solution] C++ std::format Error — Format String Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;std::format&lt;/code&gt; error occurs when the format string is malformed — such as mismatched argument count, invalid format specifiers, or unmatched braces. This throws &lt;code&gt;std::format_error&lt;/code&gt; at runtime (or causes compile-time errors when the format string can be validated at compile time in C++20).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="why-stdformat-errors-occur"&gt;Why std::format Errors Occur&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common causes include mismatched number of arguments and format placeholders, unescaped curly braces in format strings, invalid format specifiers for the given type (e.g., &lt;code&gt;{:d}&lt;/code&gt; for a string), and nested format strings with incorrect nesting.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] fmt Format String Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/fmt-error-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/fmt-error-v2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="fmt-format-string-error-fix"&gt;fmt Format String Error Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fix fmt library format string errors. Handle argument mismatches, type errors, and custom format specifiers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;fmt throws &lt;code&gt;fmt::format_error&lt;/code&gt; when the format string has issues:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;fmt::format_error: argument not found
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;fmt::format_error: invalid format specifier
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Argument count mismatch
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;{} {}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Missing two arguments
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Wrong argument type for format spec
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;{:d}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;not a number&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Missing closing brace
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello {&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Using positional arguments incorrectly
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;{1} {0}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;first&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;second&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-verify-argument-counts-match"&gt;Fix 1: Verify argument counts match&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;fmt/format.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct: 2 placeholders, 2 arguments
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;string result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;{} is {} years old&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;25&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-compile-time-format-checking-fmt-7"&gt;Fix 2: Use compile-time format checking (fmt 7+)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;fmt/format.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Compile-time check catches errors at compile time
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, {}! You have {} messages.&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Bob&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-use-named-arguments-for-complex-formatting"&gt;Fix 3: Use named arguments for complex formatting&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;fmt/format.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;string result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;format(
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;{name} is {age} years old&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;arg(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;),
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; fmt&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;arg(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;age&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;25&lt;/span&gt;));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;fmt/format.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;iostream&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;struct&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; std&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;string name;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; age;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;double&lt;/span&gt; balance;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;template&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;struct&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fmt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;formatter&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;User&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; format_specs&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;char&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; spec;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;constexpr&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;(format_parse_context&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; ctx) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; ctx.end();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; format_context&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;iterator format(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; User&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; user, format_context&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; ctx) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; {
